title: Correct factory image for Android 10 - 19 or 20?
content: Pixel 3 XL - on https://developers.google.com/android/images there are two images listed for Android 10 - one is QP1A.190711.019, the other QP1A.190711.020 - is there any word as to what the difference is? In the past, sometimes the difference has been the carrier (Verizon has gotten their own image, for example)...
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3 XL
